# Smartico Fork Guide

This repository tracks community Lightdash through `upstream/main` and carries Smartico-specific behavior in `main`.

## Custom DDL changes

ALTER TABLE public.dashboard_tabs ADD smartico_enable_ai_analysis boolean NULL;
ALTER TABLE public.dashboard_tabs ADD smartico_ai_analysis_prompt varchar NULL;

